<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html{
            font-size: 70.5px;
        }

        .box{
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px solid  rgb(35, 25, 209);
            width: 2048px;
            height: 108vw;
            margin: 14px;
            background-color: lightpink;
            font-size: 200px;
        }
        .container{
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px solid  rgb(212, 16, 16);
            /* width: 2048px; */
            height: 108vw;
            margin: 12px;
            background-color: rgb(3, 126, 160);
            font-size: 60px;
        }
        .container > p{
            font-size: 2em;
            
        }
        .container > div > div{
            border: 2px solid black;
            width: 50%;

        }

        .mycont{
            border: 2px solid black;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 23px auto;
            color: rgb(0,0,0)
            font-size 22px;
            width: 80vw;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
            this is a box.
     </div>       
            <div class="container">
                <p>
                    
                      Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quis, doloribus! Officia eveniet sapiente ratione ea 
                      rem eligendi sequi exercitationem autem itaque dolore, odio nam.
                    <div>
                         Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Optio, qui doloribus libero iste distinctio, alias atque vero 
                        deserunt, eveniet cupiditate sed? Ducimus, repellendus voluptatibus!
                   </div> 
                </p>

            </div>

      
      <div class="mycont"> 
        I am a computer science student.
      </div> 
   
</body>
</html>